title: Sleeping Bear Dunes National Lakeshore: Virtual Tour
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Photos & Multimedia     Virtual Tour              Virtual Tour       The Virtual Tour is a photo gallery that provides a few highlights of the park. After seeing a few of these pictures, you will want to come and experience it in person.  There is no way we can capture all there is to do and see at Sleeping Bear Dunes National Lakeshore, but this will give you some idea of what you will find when you come to visit. To take the tour in sequence from South to North and finally to the Islands, make sure the Photo Gallery is set for Order by Title.   Â                 Virtual Tour   54 Photos  Photographs from throughout the Park starting at the southern border heading to the north and finally to the islands.
